大多數。其實也是一早可以預期的。<br />\n<br />\n若果你，或你認識的朋友有需要，請考慮一下到海外靜修。與其留在香港成為俘虜，不如到外地進德修業。<br />\n<br />\n泛民配合共產黨 收割年輕人血鏝頭 <br />\n<br />\n將區選變相維穩工具<br />\n<br />\n泛民同共產黨合作，不停叫人送頭，將未來既政敵拉哂<br />\n（以前既例子 梁天琦）<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/DJJ2iM6.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FDJJ2iM6.jpg&h=61a607e3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/HbOBod4.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FHbOBod4.jpg&h=a5c66877&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iF3xF0L.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiF3xF0L.jpg&h=8eacbd12&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/7af0PT7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F7af0PT7.jpg&h=be6717d5&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/B0AL00N.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FB0AL00N.jpg&h=ff518829&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/SYpT9T9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FSYpT9T9.jpg&h=4d3cb98b&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/iwNZk0Q.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FiwNZk0Q.jpg&h=6d4b932e&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/AimvsFR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FAimvsFR.jpg&h=07f13712&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/25/185345_69291e53a15453bbb770155a955ea4a4.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F25%2F185345_69291e53a15453bbb770155a955ea4a4.jpeg&h=e569130c&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/11/25/185352_abc3a51d84273be18a396e37ae823653.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F11%2F25%2F185352_abc3a51d84273be18a396e37ae823653.jpeg&h=